'''燕麦'''（[[学名|学名]]：{{lang|la|''Avena sativa''}}）别称'''皮燕麦'''，为[[禾本科|禾本科]][[早熟禾亚科|早熟禾亚科]][[燕麦属|燕麦属]][[植物|植物]]，是人類的主食之一，常製成[[燕麥片|燕麥片]]、{{le|大燕麥片|Rolled oats}}販售，大燕麥片也常作為[[家畜|家畜]]的飼料。燕麥是高營養成份的食物，定期食用時可以降低血液中的[[膽固醇|膽固醇]]<ref name="ajcn">{{cite journal|journal=Am J Clin Nutr|year=2014|volume=100|issue=6|pages=1413–21|doi=10.3945/ajcn.114.086108|url=http://ajcn.nutrition.org/content/100/6/1413.long|title=Cholesterol-lowering effects of oat β-glucan: a meta-analysis of randomized controlled trials|authors=Whitehead A, Beck EJ, Tosh S, Wolever TM|pmid=25411276|access-date=2017-07-16|archive-date=2017-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171113014208/http://ajcn.nutrition.org/content/100/6/1413.long|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

燕麦中所含的燕麦球蛋白（Avenin，是類似[[小麦|小麦]]中{{le|麥膠蛋白|Gliadin}}的成份）會讓少部份人有[[乳糜瀉|乳糜瀉]]症狀<ref name=Biesiekierski2017>{{cite journal | author=Biesiekierski JR | title=What is gluten? | journal=J Gastroenterol Hepatol | year=2017 | volume=32 Suppl 1 | pages=78–81 | pmid=28244676 | doi=10.1111/jgh.13703 | url=http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1111/jgh.13703/full | type=Review | quote=Similar proteins to the gliadin found in wheat exist as secalin in rye, hordein in barley, and avenins in oats and are collectively referred to as “gluten.” Derivatives of these grains such as triticale and malt and other ancient wheat varieties such as spelt and kamut also contain gluten. The gluten found in all of these grains has been identified as the component capable of triggering the immune-mediated disorder, coeliac disease. | access-date=2017-07-19 | archive-date=2017-03-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170302195832/http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1111/jgh.13703/full | dead-url=no }}{{open access}}</ref><ref name=cjgh/>。而燕麦在製造過程也常會混合到少量含有[[麸质|麸质]]的穀類，例如小麦及大麥<ref name="cjgh">{{cite journal|pmc=4904695|year=2016|author1=La Vieille|first1=S|title=Celiac Disease and Gluten-Free Oats: A Canadian Position Based on a Literature Review|journal=Canadian Journal of Gastroenterology and Hepatology|volume=2016|pages=1870305|last2=Pulido|first2=O. M.|last3=Abbott|first3=M|last4=Koerner|first4=T. B.|last5=Godefroy|first5=S|doi=10.1155/2016/1870305|pmid=27446825}}</ref><ref name=CominoMoreno2015>{{cite journal | vauthors = Comino I, Moreno Mde L, Sousa C | title = Role of oats in celiac disease | journal = World J Gastroenterol | volume = 21 | issue = 41 | pages = 11825–31 | date = Nov 7, 2015 | pmid = 26557006 |pmc= 4631980 | doi = 10.3748/wjg.v21.i41.11825 |quote= It is necessary to consider that oats include many varieties, containing various amino acid sequences and showing different immunoreactivities associated with toxic prolamins. As a result, several studies have shown that the immunogenicity of oats varies depending on the cultivar consumed. Thus, it is essential to thoroughly study the variety of oats used in a food ingredient before including it in a gluten-free diet.}}</ref><ref name=FricGabrovska2011>{{cite journal|vauthors=Fric P, Gabrovska D, Nevoral J|title=Celiac disease, gluten-free diet, and oats|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_nutrition-reviews_2011-02_69_2/page/107|journal=Nutr Rev|volume=69|issue=2|pages=107–15|date=Feb 2011|pmid=21294744|doi=10.1111/j.1753-4887.2010.00368.x|type=Review}}</ref>。燕麥含有[[植酸|植酸]]攝取過量會影響鈣、鐵、鎂的吸收，為[[骨質疏鬆症|骨質疏鬆症]]、[[貧血|貧血]]患者應注意的產品，加工製品單位熱量遠高於米飯，糊化後[[升糖指數|升糖指數]]（GI值）亦會增加。

==形态特征==
一年生[[草本|草本]]；根系发达，秆直立光滑，叶鞘光滑或被有微毛，叶舌大，没有叶耳，叶片扁平；圆锥花序，穗轴直立或下垂，向四周开展，小穗柄弯曲下垂；颖宽大草质，外稃坚硬无毛，有或无芒；[[颖果|颖果]]腹面具有纵沟，被有稀疏茸毛；成熟时内外稃紧抱子粒，不容易分离，这与[[莜麦|莜麦]]（裸燕麦）不同。

